{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CCVaEGWQjc688h4GWspKMi","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information needed. Here's my verification report:\n\n## Invariant (c) Verification Report\n\n### Status: **VERIFIED** ✓\n\nThe `timeout_cancel` instruction correctly implements both required guards.\n\n---\n\n### Finding 1: `is_expired()` Guard\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs`\n\n**Import** (line 4):\n```rust\nuse rng_shared::timeout::is_expired;\n```\n\n**Usage** (lines 57-62):\n```rust\n    // Check timeout has elapsed using shared helper\n    let now = Clock::get()?.unix_timestamp;\n    require!(\n        is_expired(coinflip_match.resolve_deadline, now),\n        CoinflipError::LockTimeoutNotElapsed\n    );\n```\n\n**Function Definition**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/timeout.rs` (lines 12-15)\n```rust\n/// Returns `true` when the current time is at or past the resolve deadline.\npub fn is_expired(resolve_deadline: i64, now: i64) -> bool {\n    now >= resolve_deadline\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Finding 2: `is_fulfilled()` Guard\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs`\n\n**Import** (line 5):\n```rust\nuse rng_shared::vrf_orao::{is_fulfilled, read_orao_randomness};\n```\n\n**Usage** (lines 64-70):\n```rust\n    // Check that VRF randomness is NOT fulfilled — if it is, must use claim_payout instead.\n    // read_orao_randomness returns Ok([u8;32]) if fulfilled, Err if not.\n    // We try to read; if it succeeds and is fulfilled, reject the timeout cancel.\n    let vrf_is_fulfilled = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)\n        .map(|r| is_fulfilled(&r))\n        .unwrap_or(false);\n    require!(!vrf_is_fulfilled, CoinflipError::InvalidPhase);\n```\n\n**Function Definition**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/vrf_orao.rs` (lines 20-23)\n```rust\n/// Returns true if the 32-byte randomness is non-zero (i.e., fulfilled).\npub fn is_fulfilled(randomness: &[u8; 32]) -> bool {\n    randomness.iter().any(|&b| b != 0)\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Guard Logic Summary\n\n**Guard 1 - Timeout Expiry** (line 60):\n- Requires `is_expired(coinflip_match.resolve_deadline, now)` to be `true`\n- Returns error `LockTimeoutNotElapsed` if timeout hasn't elapsed\n\n**Guard 2 - VRF Not Fulfilled** (line 70):\n- Requires `!vrf_is_fulfilled` to be `true` (i.e., VRF **must NOT** be fulfilled)\n- Returns error `InvalidPhase` if VRF has already been fulfilled\n- Correctly gates the cancellation path: if randomness is already available, must use `claim_payout` instead\n\n---\n\n### Invariant (c) is **SATISFIED**\nThe `timeout_cancel` instruction uses both `shared::timeout::is_expired()` AND `shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled()` guards as required, preventing timeout cancellation when the VRF has been resolved."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ae3eb56dc8f140983 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 33137\ntool_uses: 6\nduration_ms: 32134</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cccd267e-4b06-490e-a6ee-407a80f063f8","uuid":"584561d7-3bfc-4b10-ac36-fe9210348319","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the timeout_cancel instruction source file in the coinflip program. It should be at `solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs` or similar path.\n\nVerify invariant (c): `timeout_cancel` uses `shared::timeout::is_expired()` AND `shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled()` guard.\n\nCheck:\n- Does it call `shared::timeout::is_expired()` or equivalent?\n- Does it check VRF fulfillment status via `shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled()` or equivalent?\n- What are the guards before allowing timeout cancellation?\n\nAlso read:\n- `solana/shared/src/timeout.rs` for the `is_expired` function\n- `solana/sh